-- Yoox Shares Are Rated `Buy' at Berenberg Bank  for Its Global Distribution
-- Francesca Cinelli
-- 2010-07-07T06:36:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-07/yoox-shares-are-rated-buy-at-berenberg-bank-for-its-global-distribution.html

          
          
             Yoox SpA  was rated “buy” at
Berenberg Bank, which initiated coverage of the Italian Internet
fashion retailer and set a price estimate of 7.5 euros.  
 The brokerage cited a “global distribution platform,
superior product offering,” according to a note dated July 6.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
 Francesca Cinelli  in Milan at 
 fcinelli@bloomberg.net .  
          
          


  


        